-4-local-splitscreen-1851537589\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/dragon-ball-sparking-zero-tenkaichi-4-local-splitscreen-1851537589\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eBudokai Tenkaichi \u003c/em\u003eseries, \u003cem\u003eSparking Zero\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cem\u003e. \u003c/em\u003eAnd folks, there are a lot of characters in this game. A lot! There’s at least a 19 Gokus running around this arena fighter.  — Zack Zwiezen\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/dbz-budokai-4-sparking-zero-full-roster-reveal-182-goku-1851652826\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/dbz-budokai-4-sparking-zero-full-roster-reveal-182-goku-1851652826\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"bf09c031d4437cf98641cdc7686f4d7e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://bf09c031d4437cf98641cdc7686f4d7e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A man with pink hair and green earrings smiling menacingly.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A man with pink hair and green earrings smiling menacingly.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/bf09c031d4437cf98641cdc7686f4d7e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/bf09c031d4437cf98641cdc7686f4d7e.jpg\"